{"tid":2424694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<空襲敘利亞>白宮： 美國人受威脅時 有權自行選擇方式行動","createTime":"2021-02-26T19:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T19:58:44.000Z","uid":227801,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6774f3223c31ff9d02faf12050ee9857d7e8bffb","tid":2424694,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T19:02:17.000Z","msg":"白宮：在敘利亞發動空襲是要發出毫不含糊信息<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮說，通過空襲敘利亞東部伊朗支持的民兵組織目標，是要發出毫不含糊的信息。白宮發言人普薩基說，總統拜登要表明，將會採取行動保護美國人，以及當構成威脅時，他有權在自行選擇的時間和方式採取行動。五角大樓早前表示，美軍周四向發動空襲，摧毀多處設施，回應駐伊美軍接連受到火箭炮攻擊，這是拜登就任總統後首次經確認的軍事行動。根據敘利亞戰爭的監察組織說，空襲導致22名民兵組織成員死亡。<br />\n<br />\n2021-02-27 02:45:00<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577793-20210227.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577793-20210227.htm&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2Bw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=b46326d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577793-20210227.htm&h=ceaaf395\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577793-20210227.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3f135df64b8303b9ecc7ae637ed3bc1b90e7fb38","tid":2424694,"uid":362754,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T19:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaAybi0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaAybi0.jpg&h=53077e63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd7061d82f636a662b84165fae0f5592ffb26109","tid":2424694,"uid":161440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T19:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e2bc122fc5b59759d12e8e5274490628860469","tid":2424694,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3f135df64b8303b9ecc7ae637ed3bc1b90e7fb38","tid":2424694,"uid":362754,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T19:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaAyb